  <brief_title>Study of Mood Effects of Varenicline (Chantix) in Depressed Outpatient Smokers</brief_title>
  <official_title>Systematic Assessment of Response to Open-label Treatment With Varenicline in Depressed Outpatient Smokers</official_title>
